\zoli1 \bd Njia yote kwenda \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd  nifuate \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd ! Nifanane naye Bwana, niwe nuru huku! Namkiri \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  pote na katika hali zote! Mbali, kwetu, kila saa nifanane naye! \bd*
